{"type": "article", "id": 19154, "title": "“手提包”音响", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-16T07:32:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134739prn4YAKWouR3NjiZ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个“手提包”其实是一个便携式的无线音响，来自丹麦的 Vifa。它外面的一层布料是从丹麦纺织品牌 Kvadrat 订制的，能防污防泼水，兼具舒服的手感，很时尚。频率响应可达 58Hz-18kHz/±3dB 的规格，内含 2 个全音域单体、2 个中低音单体和 2 个被动幅射式单体，可选绿、粉和灰色，售价 399 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.vifa.dk/shop/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145803esyY6Bul47z9QN0I.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"572\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.95333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145804bQzk3tBEhAl2pKdP.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"1001\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145804AhvOtEFPkWzeRB6p.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"477\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145805pMKVtqbjkEXzsBWQ.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"525\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}